<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阳光咖啡厅里坐满了人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们坐在位子上喝咖啡，吃面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女人站在柜台后面。“下一位。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人走向柜台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他点了一杯茶。“请再给我一个甜甜圈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐下来，吃了一口甜甜圈。突然…….</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”杰克看着盘子里的食物，皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘校长为什么非得换菜单呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>午餐时间，罗西和她的朋友们在学校食堂里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天是换新菜单的第一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的盘子里装满了蔬菜和全麦食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有食物都是健康，有机的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔痛苦地说：“潘校长为什么要这样对我们？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>以前的菜单，除了牛肉汉堡，都非常好吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们俩真幼稚。”玛拉说，“午餐很好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉吃了一口甘蓝沙拉，笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，她又吃了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔用怀疑的眼神看着午餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用叉子叉起一个小方块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么东西？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是豆腐。”玛拉说，“它是黄豆做的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>味道不错。你应该试试。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔皱起了鼻子。“不了，谢谢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>豆腐从叉子上掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它掉在桌子上，又从桌子上弹到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个路过的同学踩碎了那块豆腐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它变得又平又黏，上面沾满了灰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和特勒尔笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢新菜单。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，潘校长不但要换菜单，她还想每个学生都变得更健康。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，她延长了十分钟休息时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个改变好！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。不过……”特勒尔叹了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿能把我们从甘蓝和豆腐中解救出来就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿有更重要的事情要做，特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，火箭女孩儿说不定还很喜欢这些食物呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔怀疑地看了罗西一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 是吗？你怎么知道？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西愣住了。“嗯…….”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上就回来。”罗西跟朋友们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到走廊，打开手表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长看起来很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么事情，市长？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！发生了可怕的事情。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 饥饿僵尸们正在入侵美罗城！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阳光咖啡厅里有一大群！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。我马上赶到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>